Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}وغد
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}!لا تستهن بنا
